article.headline: Albany 87, New Hampshire 79
article.story: WEST POINT, N.Y. (AP) -- Blagoj Janev scored 20 points to lead New Hampshire over Army 61-47 Tuesday night. Craig Walls had 13 points for New Hampshire (4-6), and Griffin Walker added nine rebounds. Marshall Jackson and Bill Mohr scored 11 points apiece for Army (3-6), while Matt Bell had 10 points and Amadou Adeniyi had nine rebounds.
